<%= @event[:notes] %>

Your <%= @event[:course_name] %> classroom has been started.

You can access the classroom master using:

  * Address: <%= @event[:address] %>
  * Dashboard: <%= @event[:dashboard] %>
  * PE Console: <%= @event[:console] %>
  * Zoom URL: <%= @event[:session_url] %>

<% windows_nodes = @event[:instance_data].reject {|node| node['password'].nil? } %>
